1. DATASET (Mendeley Data release)
-----------------------------------
The DermGAN-DDPM synthetic image dataset associated with PoxNetX: Viral Pox skin lesion dataset, published
on Mendeley Data (DOI: 10.17632/p4bst76r7w.3), is distributed under the
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License
(CC BY-NC 4.0).

