3. THIRD-PARTY SOURCE DATASETS
--------------------------------
Images used to train the generative pipeline were drawn from 16 external
source datasets, each carrying its own license. These sources are listed,
with their individual license terms and access links, in
primary_sources.md. This repository does not redistribute any original
third-party source images. One source (Ali et al., 2024) is itself
licensed CC BY-NC 4.0 upstream; its imagery is referenced by link only.
